doc.after: Vandalism is any addition removal or change of content in a deliberate attempt to compromise the integrity of Wikipedia Examples of typical vandalism are adding irrelevant obscenities and crude humor to a page illegitimately blanking pages and inserting obvious nonsense into a page Abusive creation or usage of user accounts and IP addresses may also constitute vandalism
